description: The iShares iBonds Dec 2027 Term Muni Bond ETF seeks to track the investment results of an index composed of investment-grade U.S. municipal bonds expected to mature or be redeemed before December 2, 2027.This Fund is covered by U.S. Patent Nos. 8,438,100 and 8,655,770.
name: iShares iBonds Dec 2027 Term Muni Bond ETF
